    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! \ud83d\udc4b I'm looking to find a new home for my trusty car. It\u2019s in really solid shape and has been super dependable for me\u2014runs smooth and looks great! It\u2019s perfect if you\u2019re looking for a quality ride that\u2019s been well-cared for. I\u2019d love for you to come by, check it out, and take it for a test drive. Let's get you on the road! \ud83d\ude97\u2728",
