    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "This E46 M3 represents a driver-focused example of the iconic S54-powered platform. The 3.2L naturally aspirated inline-six delivers sharp throttle response via its individual throttle bodies, pulling cleanly to the 8,000 RPM redline. Mated to a crisp 6-speed Getrag manual transmission and a factory limited-slip differential, the mechanical engagement remains tactile and precise. Recent preventative maintenance includes a comprehensive VANOS overhaul and rear subframe reinforcement, ensuring the chassis's torsional rigidity remains uncompromised. While exhibiting honest patina consistent with its mileage, the suspension geometry is dialed, featuring refreshed bushings for improved turn-in and lateral stability. This is a mechanically sound specimen ready for spirited canyon carving or high-speed touring.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 44
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_8_listing_3",
